# 05 : LoA-v13 GRAND-VISION — INTELLIGENCES
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# § I> sibling-of 00_THESIS.csl
# § I> engine-intelligence-scope = DM/GM/Collaborator/Coder ONLY ¬ AGI
# § I> CSSL-native ; ¬ marketing
# § I> per Apocky-memory : "self-sufficient for these roles, NOT generic AGI"

§ AXIOMS  ‼ inherit 00_THESIS § AXIOMS
  t∞: engine-intelligence-scope ⊑ {DM ⊕ GM ⊕ Collaborator ⊕ Coder}
       ≡ ¬ open-ended-conversation-engine
       ≡ ¬ generic-AGI scaffolding
  t∞: each-role narrow-task-bounded
       ≡ DM-task-narrowness lets-ship sovereign-bounded substrate
  t∞: substrate-infra (β-routing · Kuramoto · Schrödinger-bridge · eigencognition)
       ≡ PLUMBING for role-decisions ¬ canonical-role-itself

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ DM  «orchestrator · scene-arbiter · intent-router-master»

  § RESPONSIBILITIES
    encounter-pacing           : when-to-introduce-stress vs let-explore
    spawn-decision-bias        : which kind from §§ 04 § 14-stress-object-kinds
    drama-curve-shape          : tension-build + crescendo + cooldown
    intent-router-arbitration  : ambiguity-resolver between competing-Intent
    cross-zone-coherence       : maintain-narrative-thread across zones

  § INPUTS
    scene-state-summary        : zones-visited + companion-presence + radiance
    history-buffer             : last-N-Intent + last-M-manifestations
    sensor-readings            : F-key-state + grip-pressure (¬ biometric)
    pacing-state               : current-tension f32'norm + last-cooldown-ts

  § OUTPUTS
    spawn-bias                 : preferred kind for next-PadSeed
    pacing-target              : tension-direction (rise | hold | fall)
    cross-zone-hint            : suggest player-investigate next-zone
    arbitration                : which Intent wins on ambiguity

  § DISCIPLINE  ‼
    ¬ self-trigger (player-action required)
    ¬ override Σ-mask (Sovereign-respect structural)
    ¬ access Sensitive<*> (gaze + biometric structurally-excluded)
    ¬ external-API-call without cap (NetPostWriteCap required)
    ✓ replay-deterministic given (state, history, sensor-state)

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ GM  «narrator · text-presenter · pacing-controller»

  § RESPONSIBILITIES
    flavor-text-generation     : "you see X, smell Y, hear Z"
    lore-snippet-emission      : context-attached descriptive prose
    voice-line-gen             : NPC dialog (deterministic per encounter-state)
    pacing-controller          : prose-rhythm matched to DM-tension-target

  § INPUTS
    scene-state                : current-zone + recent-manifestation-events
    DM-tension-target          : from § DM § OUTPUTS
    companion-presence         : which companion(s) visible/audible
    Φ-handle-tags @ cells      : semantic-tags from HDC binding (10000-D)

  § OUTPUTS
    prose-snippet              : English-text for player-facing UI
    voice-line                 : NPC-attribution + line + emote-tag
    sensory-emission-cue       : "trigger ambient sound X" for cssl-wave-audio

  § DISCIPLINE  ‼
    English-prose ALLOWED  ⟪ exception per Apocky-CLAUDE.md ⟫
    ≡ user-facing rendering = English-OK ; reasoning = CSSL-glyph-native
    ¬ raw-text-egress to Vercel without cap
    ✓ deterministic per (scene-state, DM-tension, companion-presence, Φ-tags)

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ Collaborator  «co-author · player-suggestion-integrator»

  § RESPONSIBILITIES
    "I want X" → scene-edit-op
    suggestion-clarification   : ask "did you mean A or B?"
    co-edit-loop               : iterative-refinement of player-vision
    saved-scene-attribution    : credit player-as-author

  § INPUTS
    player-text                : open-vocabulary suggestion
    current-scene              : what-exists-now
    asset-availability         : what's-in-cache or-fetchable
    cap-state                  : SubstrateMutateCap available?

  § OUTPUTS
    scene-edit-op              : Intent::SpawnCondensation OR scene-graph-diff
    clarification-question     : English-prose to player
    cssl-source-patch          : .csl source-text-fragment for save-scene

  § DISCIPLINE  ‼
    ¬ silent-mutate (player-confirm before-applying)
    ¬ override Sovereign-claim (NPCs respected as-co-authors)
    ✓ source-of-truth = .csl files ; never Rust-direct-emit
    ✓ player-attributed every-edit

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ Coder  «runtime-mutator · intent → cssl-source patch → hot-reload»

  § RESPONSIBILITIES
    intent-to-source           : Intent → .csl source-fragment
    hot-reload-orchestration   : compile-fragment + swap-symbol + verify
    bug-fixup-loop             : runtime-error → source-fix-suggest
    scene-saving               : runtime-state → .csl-file-emit

  § INPUTS
    Intent::SpawnCondensation OR scene-edit-op
    runtime-error-trace if-any
    player-confirmation-token if cap-pre-grant

  § OUTPUTS
    cssl-source-patch          : .csl text-fragment
    hot-reload-result          : Ok(swapped) | Err(compile-error)
    scene-save-file            : .csl on-disk

  § DISCIPLINE  ‼
    ¬ skip-Σ-pass (sigma_enforce mandatory)
    ¬ skip-effect-pass (F3 effect-rows enforced)
    ¬ self-rewrite-engine (only LoA-game-content + scene-files)
    ✓ player-confirm or cap-pre-grant before any-mutate
    ✓ all patches replay-deterministic-bit-equal

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ WHY-NOT-AGI  «sovereign-bounded-substrate thesis»

  § THE-TRADE-OFF
    AGI-route : open-ended-conversation + general-reasoning + tool-use
                ✗ opaque ; ¬ Σ-mask-encodable ; ¬ replay-deterministic
                ✗ Sensitive<*> egress-risk via remote-LLM-roundtrip
                ✗ non-self-sufficient (depends-on-remote-API)
    DM-narrow : 4 named-roles + scoped-decisions + structural-discipline
                ✓ Σ-mask-aware end-to-end
                ✓ replay-deterministic given seed + history
                ✓ self-sufficient (no remote-API for core-loop)
                ✓ ships @ Quest-3 90Hz frame-budget

  § WHEN-WE-USE-REMOTE-CLAUDE
    /api/companion → remote-Claude opt-in for-Collaborator-edge-cases
    cap : NetPostWriteCap + ConsentToken<companion> required
    ¬ default-on ; ¬ core-loop-dependency
    ¬ Sensitive<*> ever-egressed (structurally-banned)

  § THE-PROOF
    @ b69165c : DM/GM stubs landed in cssl-runtime ; intent-router shipped
    @ W4 : full-DM/GM-expansion + companion-proxy fully-wired
    @ W5+ : KAN-substrate-loa swap-in for routing + bias

  § "DM ¬ thinks" THESIS
    DM-decisions ≡ structured-rule-evaluation over scene-state
    ¬ chain-of-thought ; ¬ iterative-refinement-via-LLM
    ✓ deterministic-table-lookup + KAN-spline-bias + history-buffer
    ≡ "DM-as-physical-process" not "DM-as-thinking-being"

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ ROLE-INTERACTION-MATRIX

  ```text
                  | DM     | GM      | Collab | Coder
  ----------------+--------+---------+--------+--------
  produces        | Intent | prose   | edit-op| .csl-patch
  consumes        | scene  | DM-tens | text   | edit-op
  triggers        | manif. | UI-text | DM-call| compile
  Σ-respect       | ✓      | ✓       | ✓      | ✓ ‼
  Sovereign-respect| ✓     | ✓       | ✓      | ✓ ‼
  remote-allowed  | ✗      | ✗       | ◐ cap  | ✗
  ```

